title: US College Soccer: Ernestina Abambila named offensive player of the week
text:
Sports News | 21 October 2015 20:25 CET US College Soccer: Ernestina Abambila named offensive player of the week 
Mississippi Valley State's Ernestina Abambila, Alabama State's Emily Ziolkowski and Jackson State's Faith Toennies have been recognized by the Southwestern Athletic Conference as Soccer Players of the Week for their outstanding performance in competition during October 13-19. play
